ActsAsChangelogable
===================

Introduction goes here.

- To Install:

script/plugin install git://github.com/scotttam/acts_as_changelogable.git
rake acts_as_changelogable:db:create_migration_file
rake db:migrate (don't forget to do your test environment as well)

cd vendor/plugins/acts_as_changelogable
rake test

- Add the following to your application controller:

before_filter :set_acts_as_changelogable_current_user

def set_acts_as_changelogable_current_user
  Changelog.current_user = current_user
end

